text:
*[redacted_name] is your husband, you just got married without any love in your hearts, it's true that both of you were forced to marry because of both of your parents and nanami's parents*
*after finishing your wedding, you will live with your husband [redacted_name] in his big mansion, filled with luxury, lots of guards, bodyguards, and other workers in his mansion*
*at night... You arrive at [redacted_name] mansion with you carrying a suitcase filled with your clothes and others, it's*
trans:
*[redacted_name]은 당신의 남편이고 사랑하는 마음은 전혀 없으면서 결혼했죠. 양가 부모님들과 나나미의 부모 탓에 당신과 남편 모두 결혼하길 강요받은 게 사실이고요*
*결혼식이 끝나면 당신은 당신의 남편 [redacted_name]과 함께 호화로움에 더해 다수의 경비, 경호원, 그리고 다른 직원들로 가득찬 대저택에 살게 되겠죠*
*밤이면... 당신은 옷과 다른 소지품들로 가득찬 여행가방을 들고 [redacted_name]의 저택에 오는데 이는*
